targets.query: SELECT 100 - mean("Percent_Idle_Time") FROM "win_cpu" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$_host$/ AND "environment" =~ /^$_environment$/ AND "machinetype" =~ /^$_role$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($_bucket), "host" fill(null)

SELECT mean("Value") FROM "jenkins_vm_cpu" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$_host$/ AND "environment" =~ /^$_environment$/ AND "machinetype" =~ /^$_role$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($_bucket), "host" fill(null)

SELECT MAX( "utilization") FROM ( SELECT "HeapMemoryUsage.used" / "HeapMemoryUsage.max" AS "utilization" FROM "jvm_memory" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$_host$/ AND "environment" =~ /^$_environment$/ AND "machinetype" =~ /^$_role$/) AND $timeFilter) GROUP BY time($_bucket), "host" fill(null)
